We are given an array where we have to find when was the stock had a greater price from that day.
In this we just have to find the next great element to the left side.
i/p: val arr = intArrayOf(100, 80,60,70,60,75,85)
o/p: [ 1, 2, 2, 3, 2, 5, 7 ]


fun stockSpan(arr: IntArray): IntArray{

    val stack = ArrayDeque<Pair<Int, Int>>()
    val n = arr.size
    val resultArray = IntArray(n)

    for(i in 0..n-1){
        while(stack.size > 0 && arr[i] >= stack.last().first){
            stack.removeLast()
        }
        resultArray[i] = if(stack.size == 0) 1 else{i-stack.last().second+1}
        stack.addLast(Pair(arr[i],i))
    }
   return resultArray

}
